{"tid":1908711,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"229 縱火案採購經理手足及荷蘭籍手足被拒保釋","createTime":"2020-03-03T12:48:14.000Z","updateTime":"2020-03-05T02:26:47.000Z","uid":240362,"like":3,"dislike":11,"uniUserReply":15,"replies":[{"pid":"a8b5fe90184b6053c7038c052735cd750e9e779f","tid":1908711,"uid":240362,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-03T12:48:14.000Z","msg":"兩名男被告依次為鄧振強（42歲，採購經理）及荷蘭籍的De Bruin Edgar Willem Aart（31歲），二人被控一項縱火罪，控罪指他於今年 2 月 29 日，在旺角山東街及洗衣街交界，無合法辯解而用火損壞香港政府一個垃圾桶，意圖損壞該財產或罔顧該財產是否會被損壞。<br />\n<br />\n案件押後至 4 月 27 日九龍城裁判法院再訊，以待進一步調查，包括檢驗手提電話及追查閉路電視錄影，主任裁判官羅德泉拒絕二人保釋申請，兩被告還押候訊。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n據了解，兩名被告在案發現場相識，案發時有警長稱發現兩名被告向路障的火堆加紙張，及後二人逃走，之後被捕。而次被告以旅客身份入境，現正申請工作簽證，以為專尋找幼稚園老師的獵頭公司工作。<br />\n<br />\n案件編號：WKCC478/2020"},{"pid":"a82923a502fefd200da6153ae32646ebe68f6f53","tid":1908711,"uid":86374,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-03T12:49:17.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"486e1af5bbf3ff710e8d75e9995c31cbb3593834","tid":1908711,"uid":195258,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-03T12:50:33.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0879e29e13a97b2534330262fa050e9e7f305115","tid":1908711,"uid":265839,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-03T12:51:30.000Z","msg":"黑狗死全族，全家肺炎死"},{"pid":"22e507b81c58083e823fca808bf6f13c1bf7da10","tid":1908711,"uid":14449,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-03T12:52:20.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"eafe4ee3dcb6d29362dec7c149cf12e22ba28add","tid":1908711,"uid":62512,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-03T12:53:59.000Z","msg":"黑警